schools.name: Dr. Henry A. Wise Jr. High School

data.description: Renovated 3-bedroom home in the desirable Town of Morningside. Gorgeous kitchen with quartz countertops and stainless appliances. Main-level bedroom and full bath. The large yard is great for entertaining with a new fence. Large detached garage with a new roof with ample space for parking or storage. Located 5 minutes from the front gate of Joint Base Andrews and minutes from I-495 and Branch Ave Metro Station, making travel to Washington DC and surrounding areas easy. Home warranty is provided. Must see!!
